    <detaileddescription>
<para>SQL catalog implementation.</para>
<para><computeroutput>SqlCatalog</computeroutput> implements the Iceberg <computeroutput>Catalog</computeroutput> API on top of a relational database. Database access goes through the <computeroutput>CatalogStore</computeroutput> interface. </para>
